                <mxCell id="13" value="&lt;strong data-end=&quot;95&quot; data-start=&quot;83&quot;&gt;Phase 1:&lt;/strong&gt; In this phase, we will begin by identifying and managing the devices that are linked and assigned to the system. This includes all PCs placed on the production lines to ensure proper visibility and monitoring. We will also verify that each PC is properly assigned to the respective employee and include all laptops allocated to employees. In the later stage of this phase, we will expand the system to include other devices such as cameras, servers, printers, scanners, and all other possible devices available in this unit." style="text;strokeColor=#82b366;align=center;fillColor=#d5e8d4;html=1;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="440" y="50" width="390" height="130" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
