                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="16" value="In this step, we will begin by identifying and working with the PCs available in stock as well as the PCs currently assigned to the production lines." style="text;strokeColor=#82b366;align=center;fillColor=#d5e8d4;html=1;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
